{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 12''' is the 12th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1632|ja|1632|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 23|ja|11月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Tadanaga|ja|徳川忠長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} were deposed. == Births == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 28th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Shunshūsui|ja|朱舜水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Confucian scholar of the Ming (* {{ill|1682|ja|1682|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Sasaki Takayuki|ja|佐々木高行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a statesman († {{ill|1910|ja|1910|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Manji|ja|万治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1658|ja|1658|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Maeda Toshitsune|ja|前田利常|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the lord of the Kaga Domain (* {{ill|1594|ja|1594|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1694|ja|1694|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the haiku poet (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiwa|ja|Meiwa|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1769|ja|1769|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Aoki Konyō|ja|青木昆陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a rangaku scholar (* {{ill|1698|ja|1698|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
