* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1632|ja|1632}}  {{ill|November 23|ja|11月23日}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光}}  and {{ill|Tokugawa Tadanaga|ja|徳川忠長}}  were deposed.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku}} 28th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1600|ja|1600}}  {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日}} ） – {{ill|Shunshūsui|ja|朱舜水}} , a Confucian scholar of the Ming (* {{ill|1682|ja|1682}} ).
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)}} 13rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1830|ja|1830}}  {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日}} ） – {{ill|Sasaki Takayuki|ja|佐々木高行}} , a statesman († {{ill|1910|ja|1910}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Manji|ja|万治}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1658|ja|1658}}  {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日}} ） – {{ill|Maeda Toshitsune|ja|前田利常}} , the lord of the Kaga Domain (* {{ill|1594|ja|1594}} ).
* {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1694|ja|1694}}  {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日}} ） – {{ill|Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉}} , the haiku poet (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644}} ).
* {{ill|Meiwa|ja|Meiwa}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1769|ja|1769}}  {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日}} ） – {{ill|Aoki Konyō|ja|青木昆陽}} , a rangaku scholar (* {{ill|1698|ja|1698}} ).

