== Deaths == * {{ill|Manji|ja|万治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1658|ja|1658|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Maeda Toshitsune|ja|前田利常|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the lord of the Kaga Domain (* {{ill|1594|ja|1594|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1694|ja|1694|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the haiku poet (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiwa|ja|Meiwa|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1769|ja|1769|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|November 9|ja|11月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Aoki Konyō|ja|青木昆陽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a rangaku scholar (* {{ill|1698|ja|1698|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
