{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月十二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 12일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 12''' is the 12th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}} , the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=}} . == Events == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1632|ja|1632|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1632|qq=}} {{ill|November 23|ja|11月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 23|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|ja|徳川家光|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Iemitsu|qq=}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Tadanaga|ja|徳川忠長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Tadanaga|qq=}} were deposed. == Births == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=}} 28th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 17|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Shunshūsui|ja|朱舜水|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shunshūsui|qq=}} , a Confucian scholar of the Ming (* {{ill|1682|ja|1682|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1682|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunka (era)|qq=}} 13rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1830|ja|1830|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1830|qq=}} {{ill|November 26|ja|11月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 26|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Sasaki Takayuki|ja|佐々木高行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sasaki Takayuki|qq=}} , a statesman († {{ill|1910|ja|1910|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1910|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Manji|ja|万治|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Manji|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1658|ja|1658|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1658|qq=}} {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 7|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Maeda Toshitsune|ja|前田利常|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maeda Toshitsune|qq=}} , the lord of the Kaga Domain (* {{ill|1594|ja|1594|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1594|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1694|ja|1694|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1694|qq=}} {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November 28|qq=}} ） – {{ill|Bashō|ja|松尾芭蕉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bashō|qq=}} , the haiku poet (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiwa|ja|Meiwa|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiwa|qq=}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill