q=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} [[:en:November 17|November 17]] ） – [[:en:Zhu Zhiyu|Shunshūsui]] , a Confucian scholar of the Ming (* {{ill|1682|ja|1682|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1682|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Bunka|Bunka (era)]] 13rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1830|ja|1830|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1830|qq=}} [[:en:November 26|November 26]] ） – [[:en:Sasaki Takayuki|Sasaki Takayuki]] , a statesman († {{ill|1910|ja|1910|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1910|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Manji (era)|Manji]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1658|ja|1658|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1658|qq=}} [[:en:November 7|November 7]] ） – [[:en:Maeda Toshitsune|Maeda Toshitsune]] , the lord of the Kaga Domain (* {{ill|1594|ja|1594|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1594|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=}} 7th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1694|ja|1694|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1694|qq=}} [[:en:November 28|November 28]] ） – [[:en:Matsuo Bashō|Bashō]] , the haiku poet (* {{ill|1644|ja|1644|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1644|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiwa|ja|Meiwa|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiwa|qq=}} 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1769|ja|1769|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1769|qq=}} [[:en:November 9|November 9]] ） – [[:en:Aoki Konyō|Aoki Konyō]] , a rangaku scholar (* {{ill|1698|ja|1698|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1698|qq=}} ).
