]] 9th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1632|1632]] [[:en:November 23|November 23]] ） – [[:en:Tokugawa Iemitsu|Tokugawa Iemitsu]] and [[:en:Tokugawa Tadanaga|Tokugawa Tadanaga]] were deposed. == Births == * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 28th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1600|1600]] [[:en:November 17|November 17]] ） – [[:en:Zhu Zhiyu|Shunshūsui]] , a Confucian scholar of the Ming (* [[:en:1682|1682]] ). * [[:en:Bunka|Bunka (era)]] 13rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1830|1830]] [[:en:November 26|November 26]] ） – [[:en:Sasaki Takayuki|Sasaki Takayuki]] , a statesman († [[:en:1910|1910]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Manji (era)|Manji]] 1st year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1658|1658]] [[:en:November 7|November 7]] ） – [[:en:Maeda Toshitsune|Maeda Toshitsune]] , the lord of the Kaga Domain (* [[:en:1594|1594]] ). * {{ill|Genroku|ja|Genroku|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Genroku|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 7th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1694|1694]] [[:en:November 28|November 28]] ） – [[:en:Matsuo Bashō|Bashō]] , the haiku poet (* [[:en:1644|1644]] ). * {{ill|Meiwa|ja|Meiwa|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiwa|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1769|1769]] [[:en:November 9|November 9]] ） – [[:en:Aoki Konyō|Aoki Konyō]] , a rangaku scholar (* [[:en:1698|1698]] ).
