* {{ill|Kan'ei|en|Kan'ei|WD=Q1192913|lt=Kan'ei|1=Kan'ei}} 9th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1632|en|1632|WD=Q6865|lt=1632|1=1632}}  {{ill|November 23|en|November 23|WD=Q3021|lt=November 23|1=November 23}} ） – {{ill|Tokugawa Iemitsu|en|Tokugawa Iemitsu|WD=Q314481|lt=Tokugawa Iemitsu|1=Tokugawa Iemitsu}}  and {{ill|Tokugawa Tadanaga|en|Tokugawa Tadanaga|WD=Q1135700|lt=Tokugawa Tadanaga|1=Tokugawa Tadanaga}}  were deposed.
